message.body: Hi! Still on for dinner!? No pressure, I'm free all week (except for Thursday) and all next week!
Ya tomorrow right? I was just about to do some shopping actually
Tell me what to bring! If you don't tell me anything, I'll bring wine
Maybe I'll attempt to prepare a dessert
Dessert would be great as it's not my specialty. i'm gona make ropa vieja i believe
Perfect!! I'll take care of dessert - how many people should I make it for??
I think it might just be the two of us actually. Hope yr hungry!
Haha ok! Yes I'm always hungry nom nom
